<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb495cbde-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s242q–5"><num value="242q–5">§ 242q–5.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For the purpose of carrying out sections 242q to 242q–5 of this title, there are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1991 through 1993.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb495cbdf-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/557/tIII/s305">Pub. L. 101–557, title III, § 305</ref>, formerly § 306, <date date="1990-11-15">Nov. 15, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/2770">104 Stat. 2770</ref>; renumbered § 305, <ref href="/us/pl/109/482/tI/s104/b/3/B">Pub. L. 109–482, title I, § 104(b)(3)(B)</ref>, <date date="2007-01-15">Jan. 15, 2007</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/3694">120 Stat. 3694</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idb495cbe0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idb495cbe1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idb495cbe2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was enacted as part of the Home Health Care and Alzheimer’s Disease Amendments of 1990, and not as part of the Public Health Service Act which comprises this chapter.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idb495cbe3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/101/557/s305">section 305 of Pub. L. 101–557</ref> was renumbered section 304 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s242q–4">section 242q–4 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
